						<div class="postbody">1.  I found the explanations to be confusing, too.  There's nothing special about the data format, but what was helpful to me was just to disassemble the internal ROM of the SPC.  It's only 64 bytes I think, you can extract it from any .SPC file.  I found the code much easier to follow than any explanations of the loading process.  You only need to use that once, then you can communicate any way you want (from within your loaded code).</div>

